
# system directory

Contains system related configuration. Roughly equal to what `configuration.nix` does in a default installation.

## system/device

- Contains hardware / device specific system configuration files which can be shared across different hosts.

## system/hosts

- Individual installations of NixOS which use this configuration.

## system/shared

- Shared system configurations.

## system/users

- Individual user based **system** configurations.
- If you want to modify their user configurations see /home.
